{
  "stem": "1826.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 221.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the fact that after the war that saw six million people were killed, and a guy like this still has this kind of feeling, you know, this kind of-- of feeling.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had-- I had other situations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When-- when I was liberated, the first-- the first-- I walked in the Russian, and two Russian colonels, whatever they were, big shots were walking, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I-- I walk this way, and they walk, like, the other way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one looks at me, and I looked at him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of them was Jewish, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said to me that I was the first Jew he met since Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yeah, this was--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there are situations with the-- the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, what they did, their own thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were against Russia, historically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Historically.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were occupied for centuries by Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they expected the Germans to be-- to liberate them, to create a Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now they have it now, but at that time, they were meeting the-- the Germans with flowers, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But later they convinced themselves that the armies were beating them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw myself one of the German officers beating a Ukrainian policeman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they-- they-- they-- the Germans had a philosophy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was reading there a-- there was a magazine, that was published by Goebbels.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You heard about Goebbels.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was the minister of propaganda.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they considered all-- all Slavic nations like slaves for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They should work for the Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this is a-- a German magazine during the occupation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was available.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was available.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was during the occupation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
